HARD TO COME BY in a bit tight at the break as well, also lacked any early foot, moved toward the inside late in the final turn, improved position as well with some mild energy late. PINE COVE in the second flight outside, stopped four wide far turn, jogged in. LEOLA traffic into the first turn, headed up the second group for a half, also stopped and was jogged in.
